The rare disease a man suffers from
American Nick Hess was haunted by his family as an alcoholic, his wife even filming him when he was dizzy, he could barely stand, and his words were hard to understand.
Although the 35-year-old man said he did not drink alcohol, it was apparent that he was drunk.
When she first accused me of being drunk without drinking, I thought she was crazy.
