After years of unnumbered investigations, it was discovered that Nick suffers from an extremely rare disease, Auto-brewery syndrome.
Basically, the body causes all the carbohydrates consumed to ferment, turning into alcohol.
The one who suspected that this might be Nick's illness was his own wife.
The disease hasn’t been cured yet, but since he gave up carbohydrates, Nick hasn’t had such episodes.
